# Graphify Instructions
You have access to the `graphify` tool via its CLI or MCP server (if configured). When answering questions about the codebase structure, discovering knowledge, or finding relationships, use the `graphify` tools (like `query_graph`, `get_node`, etc.) to query the `graphify-out/graph.json` generated for this project.

This ensures you save context tokens instead of reading large or numerous files. 
Do not read the entire codebase manually unless specifically required to perform edits that graphify cannot facilitate.
